DISCIPLINARY CASES

2010-0316. Disciplinary Counsel v. Shaw.

It is ordered by this court, sua sponte, that Kenneth Norman Shaw, Attorney Registration No. 0005525, last known business address in Warren, Ohio, is found in contempt for failure to comply with this court’s order of September 23, 2010, to wit: failure to file an affidavit of compliance on or before October 25, 2010.
